data.description: Welcome HOME! This Mila floorplan is 4 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms and has a separate office and formal dining room! This Move-In ready home has been meticulously cared for with brand new interior paint, New LVP flooring in the living areas, Wi-Fi Front and Backyard Irrigation Systems, Whole Home Gas Generator for Peace of Mind, Fully Fenced yard that Backs up to Greenspace for Privacy, Insulated Sunroom that is Heated and Cooled, Screened in Back Porch, Large Shed for your Storage Needs, Multiple Exterior Cameras with Night Vision, French Drawer Refrigerator with Icemaker, Whole House 2 Stage Surge Protector, Gourmet Kitchen with Gas Cooktop and Built in Oven & Microwave, Upgraded Interior and Exterior Lighting, 5ft Tile Shower in Primary Bathroom, Tray Ceilings In Primary Bedroom, Living Room, Formal Dining Room and Foyer, Oversized Laundry Room with Sink, PLUS SO MUCH MORE! Located in the Stonebridge Neighborhood with tons of amenities such as Basketball Courts, Tennis Courts, Bocce Ball, Putting Green, Wiffleball Court, Soccer Field, Playground, and TWO pools! Seller to provide a transferable home warranty with Choice Home Warranty that expires in December 2028 AND $10,000 towards Closing Costs.
